title: Chicken Invaders collection
description:
Here we have Chicken Invaders collection I made by now. 

Contains:
1. Chicken Invaders 1 - full version
2. Chicken Invaders 2 - full version
3. Chicken Invaders 2 Xmas - comes in .zip and needs to be unziped to play, double-click on ChickenInvaders2Xmas.exe to play
4. Chicken Invaders 3 - requests serial to be activated, how to get serial is explaind in Chicken Invaders 3 Readme.txt

It is tested and virus free.
All of it.
